title: Unlmited Dong Works
body:
( ͡° ͜ʖ ͡°) I am the bone of my Dong. ( ͡° ͜ʖ ͡°)
 
  (  ͡° ͜ʖ ͡°) Elo is my body and Memes are my blood. ( ͡° ͜ʖ ͡°) 
 
( ͡° ͜ʖ ͡°) I have created over a thousand Dank Memes. ( ͡° ͜ʖ ͡°)
 
 ( ͡° ͜ʖ ͡°) Unknown to Death, Nor known to Challenjour. ( ͡° ͜ʖ ͡°)

 ( ͡° ͜ʖ ͡°) Have withstood great LP loss to gain many elo. ( ͡° ͜ʖ ͡°)
 
    ( ͡° ͜ʖ ͡°) Yet, these hands will never hold my waifu. ( ͡° ͜ʖ ͡°)
 
        ( ͡° ͜ʖ ͡°) So as I pray, Unlimited Dong Works. ( ͡° ͜ʖ ͡°)
